[I] Crawl urls and scan for security relevant information

[T] Take a list of domains, crawl urls and scan for endpoints, secrets, api
[T] keys, file extensions, tokens and more.

[U] https://github.com/edoardottt/cariddi

[A] Edoardo Ottavianelli
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[C] extra/security
[F] CROSS

[L] GPL
[V] 1.4.6

